name: El Bombardeo
description:
"El Bombardeo" is the first work in a collection titled Exodus.  

The 111vNN algorithm, used on this work, by analyzing photos and paintings depicting the drama of wars and mass exoduses, through the centuries, is trained to reinterpret these dramatic events.

The 111vNN algorithm is a rewritten and completely revised version by me that borrows and modifies algorithms used for neural networks.

(just a curiosity.Although the title mentions a famous Picasso's work, it is not present in the set of works analyzed by the algorithm)

3800x2160 300dpi
